title: Shahid recounts the racism his family experienced after 9/11

media:group.media:title: Shahid recounts the racism his family experienced after 9/11
media:group.media:description:
Shahid, a participant in our “Being Asian in America” documentary, recounts the racism his family experienced in the aftermath of 9/11. 

This video is part of our “Being Asian in America” project. 
Watch the full documentary here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LIIvqJDv6_4 
For more on the project, visit https://www.pewresearch.org/BeingAsianInAmerica
